<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-6087] Scanning plugin.path needs to support relative symlinks</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-6087</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>
&lt;p&gt;Discovery of Kafka Connect plugins supports symbolic links from within the &lt;tt&gt;plugin.path&lt;/tt&gt; locations, but this ability is restricted to absolute symbolic links.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s essential to support relative symbolic links, as this is the most common use case from within the plugin locations. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
